誕生、成長、その一瞬一瞬が家族の宝物になりますように。

column1: 足置きを外した奥行き:53.5cm
耐荷重：座面約80kg　足置き約50kg[商品重量]5.6kg[梱包サイズ]幅55×奥行き47×高さ78cm[梱包重量]6.5kg[生産国]ベトナム[特徴]お子様の成長に合わせて高さ調節ができるチェア「E-Toko(いいとこ)」のリモデルバージョン。
お子様が通常のダイニングチェアに座ると足が床に届かず、足をぶらぶらとさせて集中力が長続きしない経験はありませんか？
また足が踏ん張れないため、上半身が傾いて姿勢が悪くなるのも気になります。
このチェアは人間工学の研究から学習に最適な姿勢がとれる様にデザインされていて、正しい姿勢で食事や学習をする習慣が身に付きます。
従来版から背当たり部分を布張りに変更したことで、長時間座っても疲れにくく、高さ調節がスムーズになりました。
ナチュラルな素材感とシンプルなフォルムで、子供部屋の学習椅子としてはもちろん、ダイニングテーブルに合わせてお使いいただけます。
・人間工学に基づいたデザイン
1200人の体型データから各身長ごとの体型サイズを統計分析し、95％のお子様の体型に合せる事を可能にしました。
座面が8段階、足置きが8段階に調節可能。座面の奥行きも連動して調節されます。
木目の美しい天然木（オーク）を使用。ナチュラルな風合いで、リビングやダイニングのインテリアになじみます。
・ダイニングで使えるデザイン
大人用のダイニングチェアと並んでも違和感のないシンプルなデザイン。リビング学習におすすめです。
足置きがついているので、勉強時に足をぶらつかせることがなく学習に集中できます。
足置きを取り外せるので、お子様から大人まで幅広く長くお使いいただけます。
座った際に背もたれが背中にフィットする曲線デザイン。背当たり部分を布張りに変更し、さらに座り心地がよくなりました。
内側にスライド金具がつき、従来版と比較して高さ調節がスムーズになりました。
■座面高さ別適応身長めやす
・上から8段目…160～170cm[組立て]完成品[対象年齢]6歳頃～大人

The Pria 85 is the only premium convertible car seat that offers a first-class ride from 14-85 pounds. Featuring CosiComfort, the premium fabrics and padding ensure the most comfort for your child. Surround your baby in comfort with the Pria 85 Convertible Car Seat, the only convertible car seat rated to 85 pounds. The Pria 85 is the only premium convertible car seat that offers a first-class ride from 14-85 pounds. Featuring CosiComfort, the premium fabrics and padding ensure the most comfort for your child. The Pria 85 is also specially designed to fit better in your car, allowing for more room for your passengers to stretch out in the front seats. It fits your real life too. Keeping the Pria 85 clean is simple. The seat pad unsnaps and removes easily over the frame. There's no need to remove the seat from the car or for complicated maneuvers with the harness straps. When the pad's clean, it's easy to replace and again, there's no need to uninstall the car seat to do it. The Pria 85 seat pad is also both machine washable and dryer safe. All this allows you to get a thorough clean not available in other car seats. Getting your child in and out of the Pria 85 has been simplified, with handy harness holders to keep the harness straps out of the way. It fits children rear-facing starting at 14 pounds and keeps them cozy up to 40 pounds. When they're ready to ride forward-facing, turn this car seat around to safely fit children up to 85 pounds
column2: the highest weight range offered by a convertible car seat. Both stages benefit from the safer side impact protection provided by Air Protect technology which protects your child where it's needed most, around the head.<div id=""shipping_info"">

The Cosco Scenera NEXT is simply a smarter car seat - designed for families who know what they need. It keeps kids safer with Side Impact Protection built into the headrest and a five-point harness that adjusts easily from the front of the seat. The harness features five heights and three buckle locations so you can be sure you're giving the best fit to your growing child. If your chosen vehicle happens to be an airplane, the Scenera NEXT has got you covered. Certified for use on aircraft, it gives your child a familiar seat during the flight. The lightweight and compact design also gets you through the airport without weighing you down. With kids in the car, messes happen. Now, thanks to the easy-to-clean car seat pad, there's no need to stress. The pad comes in a wide range of styles and colors, all of which remove from the seat and are both machine washable and dryer safe. There's also no more scrubbing goopy build-up from inside the cup holder

Quinny Zapp Xtra Mico AP Travel SystemThe next generation of the Zapp Xtra - new integrated design folds with the seat on! Ultra compact stroller folds with seat on. Features ""memory"" fold buttons, reversible seat that reclines to multiple positions with one hand, expandable canopy and storage basket. Includes transport strap with new carry handle.The Mico AP you love just got even better! Still the lightest infant car seat in its class, the updated seat features new, self-wicking fabric that deodorize and draw liquids away from the skin to keep baby dry and comfortable during the ride. The innovative seat pad design allows for removal within seconds
column2: no rethreading of harnesses required! The seat fabrics are also both machine washable and dryer safe, making removal for a thorough cleaning quicker and easier than other car seats.The ergonomic handle provides extra comfort for parents while carrying this lightweight seat. This patented cushion system provides extra protection around your baby's head, where it's needed most. The Mico AP also includes an adjustable base with LATCH for a better fit in your car. The comfortable premium fabrics and padded 5-point harness covers keep baby secure and cozy during the ride, and the included Cozi-Dozi head insert is perfect for the extra support needed by infants. Each Mico AP comes complete with a multi-position sun canopy with a flip out visor to help protect baby's sensitive eyes from bright lights.
